===Etymology===
First attested in 1541.<ref name=CH/> {{borrowing|frm|abdomen|lang=en}}, {{borrowing|la|abdomen|nocap=1|lang=en}}, possibly from {{m|la|abdō||conceal}}, from {{term|ab||away|lang=la}} + {{term|dere||to put, place|lang=la}}.<ref name=CH>{{R:CDOE|page=2}}</ref>

===Pronunciation===
